				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">What game is it, and why does it need to become UNROM?  MMC3 donor cartridges aren't that rare.
<br />
<br />Hacking Arabic-translated Kunio-kun games to be UNROM or MMC1 is out of the question.  They are dependent on features of MMC3 such as CHR-ROM being quickly switchable, the scanline counter, the 8k bankswitching size, etc.  You might be able to change it to a more capable mapper, like FME7, VRC6, MMC5, etc, but not to anything less capable.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
